---
title: Spinach Pesto Spaghetti with Chicken Note: Food processor required
description: This extra-green spin on traditional pesto doesn’t require any basil! Using a food processor (or blender), you’ll blitz spinach, Parmesan, pistachios, garlic, lemon, and olive oil into a tangy-savory-umami flavor explosion. Toss with spaghetti and juicy seared chicken, add a pinch of chili flakes if you like, and boom! It’s pesto pasta perfection!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66955fb0b0a47382be87031f-7422304b.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/66955fb0b0a47382be87031f-en-US.pdf
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/spinach-pesto-spaghetti-with-chicken-66955fb0b0a47382be87031f
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
  calories: 930 kcal
  fat: 44 g
  saturated fat: 9 g
